'''''Ultimate Guinness World Records''''' is a UK television show on [[Challenge (TV channel)|Challenge]] which was broadcast in 2004. The show features clips from 1999—2012 of ''[[Guinness World Record]]'' attempts.  A similar show, New Zealand UGWR, airs in New Zealand.

